## Third-party libraries

This project bundles the following third-party open-source libraries (all
compatible with MIT):

- Leaflet 1.9.4 — BSD-2-Clause © 2010-present Volodymyr Agafonkin, CloudMade
  https://github.com/Leaflet/Leaflet
- leaflet-polylineDecorator — MIT © Benjamin Becquet
  https://github.com/bbecquet/Leaflet.PolylineDecorator
- fflate 0.8.2 — MIT © 2020 Arjun Barrett
  https://github.com/101arrowz/fflate

Map tiles:
- Esri World Imagery / World_Shaded_Relief / World_Boundaries_and_Places —
  Please respect Esri's terms of use for the ArcGIS Online basemap services.
